snippet.title: Fast:Run - Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist now: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2263380/FastRun/

Fast:Run is a fast-paced racing game that puts your reflexes and speed to the test. In this game, your aim is to finish the levels as quickly as possible without dying.
